    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你穿行在海伍德庄园幽暗的走廊中，鲜血将为你指引真相的方向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >查尔斯·道尔顿登场——一位专精于血迹分析的法医专家，受命前往被冰雪覆盖的海伍德地区，调查多起神秘失踪事件。他必须运用自己的专业技能揭开隐藏在证据背后的真相。在那座古老的都铎式宅邸中，雾笛低鸣。你，并不孤单。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062610/extras/7a567bda6d865343d29ad7b3b1b5f207.poster.avif?t=1770311270\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062610/extras/7a567bda6d865343d29ad7b3b1b5f207.webm?t=1770311270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062610/extras/7a567bda6d865343d29ad7b3b1b5f207.mp4?t=1770311270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们以现实中法医分析师的工作为灵感，设计了能够让玩家理解并揭示证据真相的游戏机制。在《她要离开》的旅程中，你将逐渐意识到，从一开始，你就是被盯上的目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你手持电击枪，选择权在你手中——是逃避、躲藏，还是迎面而上？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062610/extras/dbf69fb3f73775658fb05b330d0f0232.poster.avif?t=1770311270\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062610/extras/dbf69fb3f73775658fb05b330d0f0232.webm?t=1770311270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062610/extras/dbf69fb3f73775658fb05b330d0f0232.mp4?t=1770311270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏环境</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从昏暗幽深的古宅走廊，到迷雾笼罩的海伍德码头，踏上这段穿越手工打造环境的旅程，搜寻对你至关重要的线索。务必仔细搜查每一个角落，每一个细节背后，都隐藏着一段故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062610/extras/7533d57052bb815ee7ddc25f048ba89a.poster.avif?t=1770311270\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062610/extras/7533d57052bb815ee7ddc25f048ba89a.webm?t=1770311270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062610/extras/7533d57052bb815ee7ddc25f048ba89a.mp4?t=1770311270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“谋杀很少是毫无意义的，它总是有所指。”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——查尔斯·道尔顿</p>",
